MTN/VDF fiber interconnection at Kintampo

2.	MTN Fibre Assets (Kumasi  Tamale)


2.1	MTN will build an underground ducted fibre route between Kumasi (lat 0640'26.11"N,
 long 00137'8.97"W) and Tamale (lat 0925'4.80"N, long 00051'36.05"W) together with seven (7) access points located as listed in  Appendix (C). The approximate length of this route is 481km.
